Package: terrainr
Type: Package
Title: Retrieve and Transform USGS Heightmaps
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Michael",
           family = "Mahoney",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mike.mahoney.218@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2402-304X"))
Description: This package aids users in retrieving and manipulating USGS 
    heightmaps, making it trivial to produce tiled images of areas of interest
    which can then be imported into 3D rendering programs such as Unity.
